data.description: Welcome to the highly coveted Subdivision of Shadow Moss. Located steps from all the amenities Beaufort has to offer (and a stone's throw from Parris Island)- this tastefully upgraded & lovingly maintained beauty is everything you've been searching for both inside and out. One of the most sought after single story plans with a bonus loft/4th bed upstairs plus a generous master suite off the back of the house offering privacy to its owners. The massive open floor plan and souring vaulted ceiling will leave your guests wowed at every turn. Dark wood cabinets, new LED lighting, and fresh paint throughout the main areas bring it a modern feel. The master is outfitted with brand new tile & mirrors in the bath; new carpet throughout the closet/bed area. Don't miss this stunner- go & show!
